data.description:
Constructed in 2018 3 level, 3 or 4 bedroom. 3.5 bath single family home on a corner lot in water privileged Carrollton Manor community of Severna Park. Spacious master suite and 2 additional bedrooms all with ceiling fans and a second full baths on the upper level. Open plan kitchen dining and living room on the first floor and fully finished basement with either a family room or fourth bedroom with full bath. Fully fenced back yard, deck and attached one car garage. 

Pet Information
Cat : Yes
Dog : Yes
